Wanzhi.

94
00:05:54,480 --> 00:05:55,040
Wanzhi.

95
00:05:58,159 --> 00:05:58,800
Wanzhi.

96
00:05:59,360 --> 00:06:01,720
I know we've had some misunderstandings lately.

97
00:06:01,720 --> 00:06:02,920
But between me and Miss Gu,

98
00:06:02,920 --> 00:06:04,450
