102
00:06:08,680 --> 00:06:10,240
and impress your mother.

103
00:06:11,440 --> 00:06:12,080
Wanzhi.

104
00:06:12,680 --> 00:06:13,480
Being with you

105
00:06:14,000 --> 00:06:15,840
isn't just about having a casual relationship.

106
00:06:15,840 --> 00:06:17,200
I truly want to marry you

107
00:06:17,200 --> 00:06:19,260
and spend the rest of my life with you.

108
00:06:20,560 --> 00:06:21,560
That day at your house,

109
00:06:21,560 --> 00:06:24,020
I took everything your mother said to heart.

110
00:06:24,120 --> 00:06:25,680
Everything I've been doing lately

111
00:06:25,680 --> 00:06:27,280
and all the effort I've put in

112
00:06:27,480 --> 00:06:29,200
is to give you a happy life.

113
00:06:30,520 --> 00:06:32,680
