Wanzhi.

118
00:06:39,560 --> 00:06:40,520
Wanzhi.

119
00:06:47,640 --> 00:06:48,440
Hello, ma'am.

120
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:52,400
Is Wanzhi home?

121
00:06:52,880 --> 00:06:54,480
I have something to tell her.

122
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:55,240
Lin.

123
00:06:55,960 --> 00:06:57,820
