124
00:06:57,840 --> 00:06:59,500
Please come back another day.

125
00:07:21,680 --> 00:07:24,240
Honey, is this your boyfriend?

126
00:07:46,640 --> 00:07:47,560
Lin Dongfeng.

127
00:08:03,440 --> 00:08:04,280
Lin Dongfeng.

128
00:08:06,120 --> 00:08:08,000
Don't come looking for me anymore.

129
00:08:08,000 --> 00:08:09,600
I don't want to see you again.

130
00:08:09,760 --> 00:08:11,080
Let's break up.

131
00:08:40,600 --> 00:08:42,000
Throw the ball over here.

132
00:08:44,760 --> 00:08:46,240
I'm talking to you.

133
00:08:46,240 --> 00:08:47,100
Did you hear me?

134
00:08:48,320 --> 00:08:50,200
