138
00:08:56,240 --> 00:08:56,840
Stop it.

139
00:09:01,680 --> 00:09:02,360
Stop!

140
00:09:02,760 --> 00:09:04,690
What gives you the right to hit him?

141
00:09:05,400 --> 00:09:06,060
Who are you?

142
00:09:06,760 --> 00:09:08,040
Mind your own business.

143
00:09:08,040 --> 00:09:09,040
Get lost.

144
00:09:09,560 --> 00:09:10,920
Or I'll beat you up too.

145
00:09:12,080 --> 00:09:12,440
Boss.

146
00:09:13,200 --> 00:09:14,160
This woman...

147
00:09:14,160 --> 00:09:14,960
She's that...

148
00:09:20,280 --> 00:09:21,610
You got lucky this time.

149
00:09:21,640 --> 00:09:22,170
Let's go.

150
00:09:28,840 --> 00:09:29,680
Are you okay?

151
00:09:42,040 --> 00:09:42,920
Thank you.

152
00:09:43,920 --> 00:09:45,320
But do we know each other?

153
00:09:45,360 --> 00:09:46,400
You don't know me,

154
00:09:46,840 --> 00:09:47,680
but I know you.

155
00:09:48,400 --> 00:09:49,680
My name is Yang Jingshu,

156
00:09:49,680 --> 00:09:50,880
from the Medical School.

157
00:09:50,880 --> 00:09:52,120
I was there that day

158
00:09:52,240 --> 00:09:54,570
at your science innovation competition.

159
00:09:54,640 --> 00:09:55,700
Why did you help me?

160
00:09:57,440 --> 00:09:58,040
Because

161
00:09:58,960 --> 00:10:00,760
you're the genius Professor Wu mentioned,

162
00:10:00,760 --> 00:10:02,400
who can change an era.

163
00:10:04,720 --> 00:10:05,520
Being a genius

164
00:10:07,120 --> 00:10:07,980
what's the use?

165
00:10:08,640 --> 00:10:10,170
I'm still looked down upon.

166
00:10:11,440 --> 00:10:12,680
Great music attracts few listeners,

167
00:10:12,680 --> 00:10:14,160
but eventually finds its audience.

168
00:10:14,160 --> 00:10:16,520
If you succeed with controlled nuclear fusion,

169
00:10:16,520 --> 00:10:18,920
it will solve the ultimate energy problem.

170
00:10:19,320 --> 00:10:20,720
Not just for our country,

171
00:10:20,720 --> 00:10:22,520
but for all humanity - it would be immeasurable merit.

172
00:10:22,520 --> 00:10:23,400
By then,

173
00:10:23,960 --> 00:10:25,490
no one will look down on you.

174
00:10:25,880 --> 00:10:28,340
You understand controlled nuclear fusion?

175
00:10:29,760 --> 00:10:31,760
Aren't you from the Medical School?

176
00:10:33,200 --> 00:10:35,560
I'm just interested in physics.

177
00:10:36,200 --> 00:10:38,080
But I only understand some of it,

178
00:10:38,640 --> 00:10:39,570
not everything.

179
00:10:41,440 --> 00:10:42,240
True.

180
00:10:42,920 --> 00:10:45,720
What difference does it make if you understand it?

181
00:10:46,280 --> 00:10:48,200
Even if I am a natural genius,

182
00:10:49,400 --> 00:10:51,200
I'm still inferior to those

183
00:10:51,200 --> 00:10:53,280
officials, businessmen, and rich kids

184
00:10:53,280 --> 00:10:55,400
with money, power, and status.

185
00:10:55,920 --> 00:10:57,320
Her mother was right.

186
00:10:57,960 --> 00:10:59,000
Education is useless,

187
00:10:59,000 --> 00:11:00,920
and research is just wasting your life.

188
00:11:00,920 --> 00:11:02,160
I'd rather have done nothing

189
00:11:02,160 --> 00:11:03,560
and still be with Wanzhi.

190
00:11:05,320 --> 00:11:06,200
Lin Dongfeng,

191
00:11:06,480 --> 00:11:07,080
you need to understand

192
00:11:07,080 --> 00:11:08,640
how great your research is.

193
00:11:09,200 --> 00:11:10,680
It will change the fate of humanity,

194
00:11:10,680 --> 00:11:12,410
not just your personal matter.

195
00:11:13,920 --> 00:11:14,780
You should know

196
00:11:14,840 --> 00:11:16,720
how many people study day and night

197
00:11:16,720 --> 00:11:18,880
just to advance technology a little bit more,

198
00:11:18,880 --> 00:11:20,740
to make our lives a little better.

199
00:11:20,880 --> 00:11:21,640
And you?

200
00:11:22,480 --> 00:11:24,000
You have the opportunity to change the world,

201
00:11:24,000 --> 00:11:25,400
yet you don't cherish it.

202
00:11:25,800 --> 00:11:27,680
If people like Einstein,

203
00:11:27,680 --> 00:11:28,120
Feynman,

204
00:11:28,120 --> 00:11:29,960
and Yang Zhenning, these stars of humanity,

205
00:11:29,960 --> 00:11:32,200
had doubted themselves because of small setbacks

206
00:11:32,200 --> 00:11:33,360
and abandoned their research,

207
00:11:33,360 --> 00:11:36,800
how would we have those brilliant moments that pushed humanity forward?

208
00:11:36,800 --> 00:11:37,880
Change the world?

209
00:11:38,760 --> 00:11:39,760
What's the point?

210
00:11:40,240 --> 00:11:41,800
I've even lost my girlfriend.

211
00:11:41,800 --> 00:11:43,080
People ahead of their time

212
00:11:43,080 --> 00:11:44,540
are destined to be lonely.

213
00:11:47,920 --> 00:11:48,480
However,

214
00:11:49,560 --> 00:11:50,820
a genius may be lonely,

215
00:11:51,000 --> 00:11:52,460
but shouldn't be fragile.

216
00:12:00,200 --> 00:12:01,800
A genius may be lonely,

217
00:12:02,960 --> 00:12:04,880
but shouldn't be fragile.

218
00:12:07,800 --> 00:12:08,680
You're right.

219
00:12:09,720 --> 00:12:10,480
Perhaps geniuses

220
00:12:10,480 --> 00:12:12,140
are born to be misunderstood.

221
00:12:13,040 --> 00:12:14,200
It's just a breakup,

222
00:12:14,200 --> 00:12:15,240
not a big deal.

223
00:12:20,600 --> 00:12:22,060
Even geniuses need to eat.

224
00:12:22,240 --> 00:12:23,280
Let's go to the cafeteria.

225
00:12:23,280 --> 00:12:24,080
It's my treat.

226
00:12:24,240 --> 00:12:25,560
How could I let you do that?

227
00:12:25,560 --> 00:12:26,620
Let me pay instead.

228
00:12:26,800 --> 00:12:28,260
I really need to thank you.

229
00:12:49,920 --> 00:12:50,920
In my opinion,

230
00:12:51,800 --> 00:12:54,130
you and Shaocheng make quite a good match.

231
00:12:54,360 --> 00:12:55,760
You two were already engaged,

232
00:12:55,760 --> 00:12:57,290
and he cares about you a lot.

233
00:13:01,240 --> 00:13:02,920
I just broke up with someone.

234
00:13:02,920 --> 00:13:05,120
Could you please consider my feelings?

235
00:13:07,000 --> 00:13:08,160
Besides,

236
00:13:08,840 --> 00:13:09,920
before my father passed away,

237
00:13:09,920 --> 00:13:12,920
he already canceled my engagement with the Gu family.

238
00:13:13,920 --> 00:13:15,780
Your father spoiled you too much,

239
00:13:16,520 --> 00:13:17,980
he completely ruined you.

240
00:13:18,520 --> 00:13:20,240
The Gu family is wealthy and prestigious.

241
00:13:20,240 --> 00:13:22,440
What's wrong with marrying Shaocheng?

242
00:13:24,240 --> 00:13:26,000
My father wasn't spoiling me,

243
00:13:26,640 --> 00:13:27,800
he loved me.

244
00:13:29,320 --> 00:13:31,080
He respected my choices

245
00:13:31,320 --> 00:13:33,380
and let me freely control my own life.

246
00:13:34,760 --> 00:13:35,760
Unlike you,

247
00:13:37,640 --> 00:13:39,570
who just wants me to be your puppet.

248
00:13:40,640 --> 00:13:42,170
How dare you talk like that!

249
00:13:43,040 --> 00:13:43,960
Explain yourself clearly.

250
00:13:43,960 --> 00:13:45,960
How have I treated you like a puppet?

251
00:13:47,040 --> 00:13:48,040
Since you were little,

252
00:13:48,040 --> 00:13:49,080
whatever you wanted to learn,

253
00:13:49,080 --> 00:13:50,040
whoever you wanted to be friends with,

254
00:13:50,040 --> 00:13:50,920
which university you wanted to attend,

255
00:13:50,920 --> 00:13:53,050
when did I ever not discuss it with you?

256
00:14:02,400 --> 00:14:04,200
Anyway, let me be clear with you.

257
00:14:04,600 --> 00:14:05,920
I'm 22 years old now.

258
00:14:06,320 --> 00:14:07,850
I can make my own decisions.

259
00:14:07,880 --> 00:14:09,320
I want to live for myself.

260
00:14:09,720 --> 00:14:11,040
I want to love freely.

261
00:14:12,360 --> 00:14:14,620
Even though I broke up with Lin Dongfeng,

262
00:14:15,040 --> 00:14:17,500
I will absolutely never be with Gu Shaocheng

263
00:14:17,640 --> 00:14:20,500
or compromise with this feudal arranged marriage.

264
00:14:23,080 --> 00:14:24,680
If my father were still here,

265
00:14:27,120 --> 00:14:28,920
he would never be like you,

266
00:14:30,720 --> 00:14:32,280
rushing to marry me off.

267
00:14:35,840 --> 00:14:37,320
Your father, your father, your father!

268
00:14:37,320 --> 00:14:39,580
You only know how to bring up your father.

269
00:14:41,960 --> 00:14:43,160
Your father is dead.

270
00:14:45,120 --> 00:14:46,160
He can't control you anymore.

271
00:14:46,160 --> 00:14:47,720
He can't control either of us anymore.

272
00:14:47,720 --> 00:14:48,780
Do you understand?

273
00:14:56,080 --> 00:14:58,040
I was hoping you could marry Shaocheng

274
00:14:58,040 --> 00:15:00,170
so I didn't want you to know about this.

275
00:15:02,400 --> 00:15:03,560
Take a good look.

276
00:15:09,160 --> 00:15:10,960
Our Zheng family has collapsed.

277
00:15:13,720 --> 00:15:16,040
These are all the debts your father left behind.

278
00:15:16,040 --> 00:15:17,640
Even this villa has been mortgaged.

279
00:15:17,640 --> 00:15:19,680
You're no longer a young lady of wealth.
